high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the fridge
Pick up spoon from the table
Move to the stove to the right of the fridge
Put spoon in the pot on the stove
Pick up pot from the stove
Move to the table to the right of the stove
Put pot on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon inside on the table to the right of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the spoon near the edge.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the stove.
Put the spoon in the pan on the top left burner.
Pick up the pan on the top left burner with the spoon in it.
Turn around and take a half step then turn left and walk until you're even with the head of lettuce on the table to your left then turn left and walk to the table.
Put the pan in the corner to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spoon in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around then turn to the left to face the white table.
Pick up the spoon in front of the blue plate on the table.
Turn right, then turn to face the stove.
Place the spoon inside the pan that it on the back left side burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the knife inside.
Turn around, then to the left, walk and turn to face the white table to your left.
Place the pan with the knife inside on the right-hand corner of the table, behind the lotion bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon inside the pan, move them to the white table.
